      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0002",
      "text": " 174",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0003",
      "text": "Vendor Identification field: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        224.33,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0004",
      "text": "The value of the Vendor Identification field shall be a T10 Vendor ID.",
      "bbox": [
        224.28,
        57.65,
        539.98,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0005",
      "text": "The format and interpretation of the Vendor Specific Data field is vendor specific to the vendor identi-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        540.02,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0006",
      "text": "fied by the value of the Vendor Identification field.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        314.38,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0007",
      "text": "Vendor Specific Data Field: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        105.64,
        227.14,
        116.76
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0008",
      "text": "The Vendor Specific Data field contains vendor specific data and shall",
      "bbox": [
        227.16,
        105.64,
        540.0,
        116.76
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0009",
      "text": "be padded to a word boundary.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        117.64,
        234.24,
        128.76
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0010",
      "text": "6.6.9",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        118.22,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0011",
      "text": "Clock Synchronization Quality of Service",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        142.96,
        323.29,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0012",
      "text": "6.6.9.1  N_Port Login",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        194.8,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0013",
      "text": "6.6.9.1.1  Applicability",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        199.87,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0014",
      "text": "The Clock Synchronization Quality of Service (QoS) field in PLOGI ELS or LS_ACC (words 62-63) is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        539.99,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0015",
      "text": "only meaningful when sent to or received from the Clock Synchronization Server (i.e., FFFFF6h).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        540.05,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0016",
      "text": "This field contains meaningful information only if either the Clock Synchronization Primitive Capable",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        539.99,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0017",
      "text": "bit of the Common features field (word 1, bit 20) is set to one; or if the Clock Synchronization ELS ca-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        539.91,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0018",
      "text": "pable bit of one of the N_Port Class Service Parameter Recipient control fields (word 1, bit 19) is set",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        540.1,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0019",
      "text": "to one.  If this field does not contain meaningful information, it shall be set to zero (see FC-FS-2).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        523.71,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0020",
      "text": "The Clock Synchronization QoS field is defined in table 174.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        361.43,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0021",
      "text": "6.6.9.1.2  CS_QoS_Request",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        225.41,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0022",
      "text": "For PLOGI and FLOGI Request, the meaning is defined in table 175.  This field is not meaningful for",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        540.06,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p193_s0023",
      "text": "PLOGI LS_ACC and shall be set to zero.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        277.04,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
